      "translation": "(1) To the protective spirit of Tarsirsir , mother Bau , her lady , Hala-Lamma , child of Lu-girizal , governor of Lagaš , ... for the well-being of Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad ."
